{'html': '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN">\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <title>Exercises Chapter 13</title>\n  </head>\n\n  <body bgcolor = "#ffffff">\n    <h1>Exercises Chapter 13</h1>\n\n1. Suppose that there is a point light source at (0.5,-2.5,4.5). The\nlight source is pure white, and there is a background ambient light of\n(R,G,B) = (0.1,0.1,0.1). The reflection coefficients for the polygon\nsurface are:\n\n<br>\nambient: (R,G,B) = (0.1,0.1,0.1)\n<br>\ndiffuse: (R,G,B) = (1,1,0)\n<br>\n\nFind an expression for  the (R,G,B) intensity for the centre of this polygon.\n\n\n    <hr>\n\n<font SIZE="-2">\n\nBack to: <a href="../../exercises.htm">Index of Exercises</a><br>\nBack to: <a href="../../chapter_13.htm">Chapter 13</a>\n\n</font>\n\n    <hr>\n<!-- Created: Tue Oct 02 09:16:49 GMT Daylight Time 2001 -->\n<!-- hhmts start -->\nLast modified: Tue Oct 02 09:34:35 GMT Daylight Time 2001\n<!-- hhmts end -->\n  </body>\n</html>\n',
